Deutsche Post Wants Right to Decide About Stamp Price, Wiwo Says

-- B y   H o l g e r   E l f e s
-- 
2011-05-07T14:17:35Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-07/deutsche-post-wants-right-to-decide-about-stamp-price-wiwo-says.html
Deutsche Post AG (DPW) , the world’s biggest
carrier of air and sea freight by volume, wants the right to
decide on postage prices instead of having to ask regulators’
approval for increases,  Wirtschaftswoche  reported today, citing
Chief Executive Officer Frank Appel.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Holger Elfes in Bonn at 
 helfes@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
